<article>
    <h1>Wo&#xAD;man, 71, hurt in 4-ve&#xAD;hi&#xAD;cle crash in Cle&#xAD;menti</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200912/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-09-12"><time>2020-09-12</time></a>
        - <span>HOME</span>
        - <span role="byline">Jessie Lim</span>
    </section>

    <p>A 71-year-old wo­man was hurt in a four-ve­hi­cle ac­ci­dent in Cle­menti yes­ter­day morn­ing.</p>
    <p>The wo­man, the driver of a car in­volved in the ac­ci­dent, was con­scious when she was taken to the Na­tional Univer­sity Hos­pi­tal, the po­lice said.</p>
    <p>The ac­ci­dent, which in­volved a taxi, two cars and a lorry, oc­curred at the junc­tion of Cle­menti Road and Ulu Pan­dan Road.</p>
    <p>The po­lice were alerted to the ac­ci­dent at 9.11am.</p>
    <p>When The Straits Times ar­rived at the scene, a red Trans-Cab taxi with a dented left front door was seen among the af­fected ve­hi­cles.</p>
    <p>Po­lice of­fi­cers were also on site to di­rect traf­fic.</p>

